From d21db735ee70d1dac07060cfc67d3bf7a4e6f83c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Matheus Sampaio Queiroga <srherobrine20@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 09:45:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] fix: prevent live context recursion and blocker races

Clone the web context before attaching the shutdown-aware request context so the original Base does not become its own context ancestor. Build blocker maps off-path and atomically publish them under an RWMutex to avoid concurrent map iteration/write crashes without holding request handling during RDAP/WHOIS refreshes.

Signed-off-by: Matheus Sampaio Queiroga <srherobrine20@gmail.com>
---
 modules/setting/blockers.go    | 30 +++++++++++++++++++++++-------
 routers/web/repo/issue_live.go | 14 ++++++++++++--
 2 files changed, 35 insertions(+), 9 deletions(-)

diff --git a/modules/setting/blockers.go b/modules/setting/blockers.go
index ff338adc97..d0161dcd9a 100644
--- a/modules/setting/blockers.go
+++ b/modules/setting/blockers.go
@@ -9,6 +9,7 @@ import (
 	"os"
